# cellPrototype

**Instance Property**

The prototype `NSCell` for displaying items in the matrices in the columns of the browser.

## Declaration

```swift
@MainActor var cellPrototype: Any! { get set }
```

## Discussion

The prototype `NSCell` instance is copied to display items in the matrices of the browser.

## Managing Component Types

- **cellClass**: Returns the `NSBrowserCell` class.
- **setCellClass(_:)**: Sets the class of the cell to be used by the matrices in the columns of the browser.
